## Internal text utilities for inspecting text primitives.

import project.Data.Text.Text
import project.Internal.Text_Helpers

## ---
   private: true
   ---
   Forces flattening of a text value.
optimize text:Text -> Text = Text_Helpers.optimize text

## ---
   private: true
   ---
   Compile the regex using the Truffle regex library.
   Returns a Java RegexObject (Truffle) (See https://github.com/oracle/graal/blob/master/regex/docs/README.md)

   ## Arguments
    - `pattern`: the regex to compile
    - `options`: string containing traditional regex flags (for example, "g" as
      in "/foo/g"
compile_regex pattern:Text options:Text = Text_Helpers.compile_regex pattern options
